---
const path = Astro.url.pathname;
const isActive = (href: string) =>
	href === '/' ? path === '/' : path.startsWith(href);
---

<div class="banner">
	<div class="banner-title">☆ The Art of Nerd ☆</div>
	<div class="banner-sub">~ theartofnerd's cyber space ~</div>
</div>

<div class="marquee">
	<div class="marquee-inner">
		◄◄ このサイトは2000年に作られました！！ Netscape で見てね！ ★ キリ番ふんだら掲示板で報告してね(^o^)/ ►►
	</div>
</div>

<div class="nav-box">
	<a href="/" class={isActive('/') ? 'on' : ''}>★ TOP</a>
	<a href="/blog" class={isActive('/blog') ? 'on' : ''}>★ BLOG</a>
	<a href="/certifications" class={isActive('/certifications') ? 'on' : ''}>★ CERTIFICATIONS</a>
	<a href="/about" class={isActive('/about') ? 'on' : ''}>★ ABOUT</a>
</div>

<style>
	.banner {
		background: #000066;
		text-align: center;
		padding: 14px 0;
		border-bottom: 3px solid #ff00ff;
	}
	.banner-title {
		color: #ffff00;
		font-size: 26px;
		font-weight: bold;
	}
	.banner-sub {
		color: #00ffff;
		font-size: 13px;
	}
	.marquee {
		background: #ff00ff;
		overflow: hidden;
		white-space: nowrap;
	}
	.marquee-inner {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 4px 0;
		color: #fff;
		font-size: 13px;
		font-weight: bold;
		animation: scroll-left 22s linear infinite;
	}
	@keyframes scroll-left {
		from { transform: translateX(100%); }
		to { transform: translateX(-100%); }
	}
	.nav-box {
		background: #ccffcc;
		border: 2px solid #009900;
		padding: 6px;
		text-align: center;
	}
	.nav-box a {
		display: inline-block;
		color: #0000ee;
		text-decoration: none;
		padding: 4px 10px;
		font-size: 14px;
	}
	.nav-box a:hover {
		background: #ffff00;
		text-decoration: underline;
	}
	.nav-box a.on {
		background: #ffcc00;
		font-weight: bold;
	}
</style>